briefdescription.para: Part variants hold information on how a part looks. It will only allow visual changes, so it will hold information regarding materials or models. A part is allowed to have mutiple variants if needed, the user can toggle this variants in the VAB/SPH when building a vessel. Or in the part selector with a small button in the corner. This class needs to be serialized so it can be copy its properties correctly to part instances.
